OL,6,FHe also admitted a charge of
OL,7,Fperverting the course of justice,
OL,8,Fwitness intimidation and offences of
OL,9,Fsupplying class A drugs.
OL,11,FNorthern Ireland's Director of Public
OL,12,FProsecutions Stephen Herron is to
OL,13,Frefer the sentence imposed by judge
OL,14,FGordon Kerr KC to the Court of Appeal
OL,15,Fon the grounds that it was unduly
OL,16,Flenient.
