OL,6,F"The sentence must not just be
OL,7,Flenient, but unduly lenient.
OL,9,F"We recognise the significant public
OL,10,Finterest in this case.
OL,12,F"However, it is important to underline
OL,13,Fthat the PPS can only refer a sentence
OL,14,Fto the Court of Appeal for
OL,15,Fconsideration when there is a legal
OL,16,Fground to do so.
