OL,4,Clenient' sentence for exploitation
OL,6,F"After careful consideration of the
OL,7,Fsentence handed down in the case of
OL,8,FOliver MacCormack, including with the
OL,9,Fbenefit of advice from independent
OL,10,Fsenior counsel, we have determined
OL,11,Fthat there is a sufficient legal basis
OL,12,Fto refer the sentence to the Court of
OL,13,FAppeal.
OL,15,F"We have taken steps to inform the
OL,16,Fvictims and the next of kin of the
OL,17,Fdeceased victim of the decision to
OL,18,Frefer the sentence.
OL,26,@nD@AOUwD@AOU
