OL,6,F"We will keep them informed of the
OL,7,Foutcome of the Court of Appeal's
OL,8,Fconsideration."
OL,10,FThere were nine victims involved in
OL,11,Fthe case, some as young as 17 at the
OL,12,Ftime of the offences.
OL,14,FOne has since died of sepsis due to
OL,15,Fintravenous drug use.
OL,17,FThe victims had vulnerabilities
OL,18,Fincluding drug addiction, homelessness
OL,19,Fand mental health issues.
