OL,6,FMacCormack was the fourth man to be
OL,7,Fsentenced following a sexual
OL,8,Fexploitation investigation conducted
OL,9,Fby the PSNI's modern slavery and human
OL,10,Ftrafficking unit.
OL,12,FAt sentencing, the court heard the
OL,13,Fvictims were heroin addicts and
OL,14,FMacCormack would exploit their
OL,15,Fvulnerability to force them into
OL,16,Fprostitution in exchange for him
OL,17,Fsupplying them with drugs.
